column3: “Picked up a gram of this done by Salish Sativa's. I am glad I did. I love Space Queen because of it's trippy high, and that carried through on this Strawberry frost. I felt like I was swirling around the world. It was also dreamy, euphoric and relaxed. Fantastic effects! I got some strawberry flavor with some citrus and just a touch of earthiness. Very tasty. It had a nice high potency too at 25.78% THC. Very nice sm...”
“Good stuff! This strain had the unusual effect of giving the ol wedding tackle a healthy buzz too.”
“Fantastic strain. Left my friends and I feeling very relaxed, uplifted, and happy. Didn't take a lot even for veteran stoners to feel lifted. Will definitely smoke again.”

“This is one of my favourite strains because it tastes amazing, and it produces a relaxation without the sleepiness, than the other strains that I have tried. I would recommend Strawberry Frost to people who are stressed, had a hard day at work, or just simply wanting to wind down before bed.”

“Grabbed a pre roll of this at Ganja Goddess in seattle! The brand Coastal* uses flower for their pre rolls and I must say I’m impressed! Very mellow but super happy and uplifting! Great for watching Netflix or playing a good RPG”

“I very strong indica , after a Tolerance break this is the strain to get back on with since it gives you that first time smoking high ! A very strong head buzz at first and a gradual sedating feeling , I rate this a 9/10 just because id wish to have this feeling but to be able to have that sativa uplifting feeling , instead of the sedation of drowsiness :)”
“Picked some of this up and it's some of the best I've had. Makes me feel really spaced out and sleepy.”
